
To load to scripts inside Vivado, there are 2 choices:

 1) Use 'package require'
    vivado% lappend auto_path <ABSOLUTE_PATH_TO_THIS_DIRECTORY>
    vivado% package require checklist
    
    Note: to remove the package from being use: 
       vivado% package forget checklist
 
 2) Source checklist.tcl script
    vivado% source -notrace <ABSOLUTE_PATH_TO_THIS_DIRECTORY>.checklist.tcl

